title: MixcMax Kitchen Plastic Chopping Board Set: Extra Thick Flexible Cutting Board Mats, Kitchen Gift with Colour Coded & Holder, Dishwasher Safe, Camping Cooking Equipment, Set of 4, Multicolour
features: COLOR-CODED CUTTING BOARD SET -- A Set of 4 Color plastic cutting boards is suitable for different food. These cutting board sets are helpful to keep the food's taste original and avoid mixing food flavours when you are cutting food. Give your family healthier meals every day.

SAFE HOME KITCHEN PREP -- The chopping board is made of high-quality food-grade materials, naturally non­stick and BPA FREE! The plastic board provides a solid surface that can be used without worrying about foods residue or leaving a knife mark. The cutting mat with a thickness of 1.3 mm can better meet the requirements of flexibility and durability.

EASY TO CARE AND STORE -- 12.2*15 inches, each large chopping board set with stand is about 115g. Easy to curl, clean, and store. Lightweight and flexible, dishwasher safe(＜90℃). Note: Please put the cutting board flat in the dishwasher. Each cutting board has a hanging hole that can be hung to save space.

TEXTURED NON-SLIP BOTTOM -- The flexible kitchen plastic cutting board have grid-textured bottom making it more stable than others, won’t slip around when keeping the counter surface dry. For wet or very slippery surfaces, just place a dampened paper towel underneath for unearthly amazing stability.

KITCHEN GIFTS & SERVICES -- This coloured chopping board set is very beautiful and practical, suitable for holiday gifts! Cooking Gifts for family, wives, mothers, friends. Please contact us if you have any questions during usage, we will offer you a satisfactory solution.
description: Product Description Dishwasher safe Our cutting mat is 100% dishwasher safe(<90°). You can put your board in the dishwasher for deep cleaning. No oiling or maintenance is required! And they don't curl up. Non-slip Each chopping board has a crosshatch textured back, so the mats will not slip on your countertop! For wet or very slippery surfaces, just place a dampened paper towel underneath for unearthly amazing stability. Flexible & Bendable Each cutting board (12"×15") is easy to store and curl to a certain angle, which is helpful to pour the chopped food directly. Great for kosher & vegetarian households!
